Components and Pages
Auth Components:

AuthProvider.tsx: Sets up Auth0 authentication provider.
withAuth.tsx: Higher-order component for protecting routes.
Usage Management Components:

Dashboard.tsx: Displays usage statistics using Recharts.
Video Library Components:

VideoPlayer.tsx: Plays videos using Plyr and Hls.js.
Transcript Components:

TranscriptEditor.tsx: Displays and edits video transcripts.
Clips Components:

ClipCreator.tsx: UI for creating video clips.
Social Media Components:

PostCreator.tsx: Rich text editor for creating social media posts.
Common Components:

Header.tsx: Common header component for navigation.
API Routes:

clips.ts: Backend route for creating video clips.
Pages:

_app.tsx: Main app component to include global styles and AuthProvider.
index.tsx: Each feature directory (usage-management, video-library, transcripts, clips, social-media) contains an index page to render respective components.
Utilities:

videoProcessor.ts: Utility for processing video clips.
